quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  3,71,"Ko onon yo yim…ďe Defte, e ko jillaŇčton kan goonga jippinaaka ka Defte mo'on e meh-re mon, hi…óon suu…óa kadi ko woni e ∆äen Defte immorde e goonga e peewal; wano sellugol Annabaaku Muhammadu on mo jam e kisiyee woni e mun, hara non hi…óon anndi goonga kan senndindiri ka e mehre nden senndindiri peewal e majjere?!"
  3,72,"Fedde goo jeyaande e karamokoo…ďe Alyahuuda en wi'i: "Gom…óinee ka fe√Ī√Īi …óon, ndee Qur'aanaare Jippinaande e gom…óim…ďe …ďen ka arannde √Īallal, yeddon …óum ka sakkitorde mayre; bela jo'o …ďe sikkitoray diina ma…ď…ďe kan sabu yeddugol mon ngol …ďaawo nde gom…óin…óon, …ďe yiltitoo hi…ďe wi'ia: ko kam…ďe …ďuri men anndu Defte Alla ∆äen, …ďe yiltike e …óum."
  3,73,"∆Āe wi'i kadi: "Wata on gom…óin jokkon si wanaa on jokkunoo…óo diina mo'on". Maaku an Nulaa…óo: "Pellet, feewugol e goonga ngol, ko Peewal Alla ngal, wanaa kon ko won…óon e mu'un e penaale". [Ko kulol fii] wata go…ó…óo goo ye…óe e …ďural yeru ngal ngal ye…óa…óon, maa kulol wennjiroygol on …óum ka Joomi moo…óon si on qirritike kon ko Jippinaa e ma…ď…ďe. Maaku an Nulaa…óo: "∆Āural ngal ko Juu…óe Alla woni, Himoye Ye…óa ngal on Mo O Muuyi e jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen, ngal ∆Āural heertinaa ki mofte …óawa go…ó…óe". Pellet, Alla ko Yaaju…óo ∆Āural, Anndu…óo on hanndu…óo e Maggal."
  3,74,"Himo Hertinana ∆Āural Makko ngal on Mo O Muuyi e Tagu Makko ngun: O Teddinira ontigi peewal e Annabaaku e noone e dokke. Alla ko Jom ∆Āural Mawngal, ngal alaa hattoode."
  3,75,"No e yim…ďe Defte …ďen, on mo halfiŇčtaa jawdi …óuu…óundi, on jonnitire ndi no timmiri; no e ma…ď…ďe kadi, on mo halfiŇčtaa jawdi see…óa, on jonnitataa ma ndin si wanaa si dari…óaa ŇčaŇčŇčan…óaa mo. ∆äum non, ko …ďe wi'irii sikke ma…ď…ďe bon…óe: "Bakkaatu alanaa men e √Īaamugol jawle Aarabee…ďe …ďen; sabu Alla Daginanii men …óum", hi…ďe ta∆īa nde fenaande takka e Alla hara hi…ďe anndi fefindagol ma…ď…ďe ngol."
  3,76,"Oo'o, huunde nde wanaa non aayordon nih, si ko woni, kala on hunnu…óo ahadi mu'un ndin e Alla: imoorde e gom…óingol Mo e Nulaa…ďe Makko …ďen, o hunni ahadi makko ndin hakkunde makko e yim…ďe …ďen o totti hoolaare, o huliri Alla jokkugol Yamirooje Makko wo…ó…óitoo Ha…óaa…ói Makko; pellet, Alla no Yi…ói …ďen huloo…ďe, O Yo…ďitiroyay…ďe …óum ko …ďuri mawnude e mbarjaari."
  3,77,"∆Āen wa…ótitiray…ďe Wasiyee Alla -Mo O Wasiyori…ďe jokkugol kon ko O Jippini ka Deftere Makko O Nuliri …óum Nulaa…ďe Makko …ďen- e woondooje ma…ď…ďe …óe …ďe woondiri hunnugol ahadi Alla ndin; hi…ďe wa…ótitira …óen woondooje e ngostiigu piiyon aduna fam…óukoy, ge…ďal alaa …ďen e mo∆ī∆īere laakara, Alla Yeewtidoytaa e ma…ď…ďe ko welata …ďe, O Ndaaroytaa …ďe ndaar…óe yurmeende √Ďalnde Darngal, hino woodani …ďe lepte muusu…óe."